Example data in the wide and long formts supported by the evoverse package.

example_input_formats.Rd

Example data in the wide and long formts supported by the evoverse package.

data(example_input_formats)

Format

4 tibbles, wide/long and mutations/copy number that show the format required to create an evoverse object with function dataset.

Examples

data(example_input_formats)
